    ===========================================================================
    
    ENHANCEMENTS AND MODIFICATIONS (2025):
    
    The following improvements were made by Penthertz:
    - Ported to Python 3 with modern library support
    - Implemented ImGui-based to modernize the graphical user interface
    - Added interactive network visualization with real-time topology mapping
    - Enhanced nonce capture and management system
    - Improved packet logging and analysis capabilities
    - Added clean exit mechanisms and better error handling
    - Modernized codebase architecture and documentation 

    Original Z-Attack tool concept and core Z-Wave protocol implementation
    by Advens (2015).
    
